        <updateDate>2021-07-21T14:15:00Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Innovation and Growth Now by Investing in Tomorrow's Enterprises Act or the IGNITE American Innovation Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows certain C corporation taxpayers to elect an increased advance refund of net operating loss carryovers attributable to COVID-19 research expenditures in 2020 and 2021. The bill also allows such taxpayers an advance refund of certain other net operating loss carryovers arising during 2015 through 2021. </p> <p>The bill allows an increased research tax credit for COVID-19 research expenditures paid or incurred on or after February 15, 2020, and before January 1, 2022.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
